quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  62,1,"Sbuccuâen Öebbi, kra illan deg igenwan, u kra illan di tmurt. Agellid, Ssid, Uzmir, Bab n ûûwab"
  62,2,"D Neppa id Iuznen i wid ur ne$ôi, Amazan segsen, iqqaô asen issekniyen iS. Izizdig iten, isselmad asen Tazmamt akked ûûwab, xas llan, zik, di ttelfan n ûûeê"
  62,3,"U i wid nniven, mara awven $uôsen. Neppa, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  62,4,"D wagi ay d lfevl n Öebbi. Ippak it i win Ib$a. Öebbi, d bab n lfevl ameqwôahan"
  62,5,"Am wid iwumi ippukelfen s Tuôa, ur p ssawven. Cuban a$yul ibubben tizmamin. I icmet umedya n ugdud inekôen issekniyen n Öebbi! Öebbi ur Inehhu ara agdud imednas"
  62,6,"Ini: \"a yudayen, ma t$ilem d kunwi ay d iêbiben n Öebbi, war imdanen, ssutret tameppant, ma tessawalem tidep"
  62,7,"Ur p ssuturen ara, d awez$i, ilmend igiten nnsen. Öebbi Issen imednas"
  62,8,"Ini: \"tameppant iwumi tregwlem, a kwen id temmager, war ccekk. Sinna, a kwen awin ar Win Iéôan ayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. Ad awen Imel ayen txeddmem"
  62,9,"A wid iumnen! Ma ssawlen d i téallit, ass unejmuâ, $iwlet ar usmekti n Öebbi, êebset ttjaôa. Ppif akka i kunwi, lemmer tessinem"
  62,10,"Mi tfukk téallit, mfaôaqet di tmurt, nadit lfevl n Öebbi, mmektit ed aîas Öebbi, amar a prebêem"
  62,11,"Mi walan ssuq, ne$ anecôeê, ad azlen $uôes, a k ooen tbeddev. Ini: \"ayen illan ar Öebbi yif anecôeê akked ssuq. Öebbi Yif akw iôeééaqen"
  63,1,"Ma usan d $uôek ixabiten, ad ak inin: \"a ncehhed ar keçç, war ccekk, d Amazan n Öebbi\". Öebbi Iéôa ar keçç, war ccekk, d Amazan iS. Öebbi ad Icehhed ar, s tidep, ixabiten d ikeddaben"
  63,2,"Ëesben tagallit nnsen d laânaya, d$a ssefôa$en abrid n Öebbi. Ihi, a yicmet wayen xeddmen"
  63,3,"Akka, acku llan umnen, sinna, jehlen. Ppusel$en wulawen nnsen, d$a nitni ur mêiûen"